Architect - Civil Site Supervision
Confidential Company -
Date Posted: 2014/05/06 08:00:09
Ref. JB3047749
Job Description
Architect - Civil Site Supervisor with min 5 years of experience with BSc./ Diploma in Architecture for one of the leading construction Company is Saudi Arabia.
Roles & Responsibilities:
Checking of drawings, comparing structural & architectural drawings, planning and ensuring availability of required drawings in time. Coordination with the clients, consultants and other team members. Ensure project design milestones are met as planned.
Candidates with transferable Iquama should only apply.
Candidate should work in Site,and supervise the work related activities and should report to Project Manager everyday.
